                    <article id="post-8464" class="kb-article-excerpt post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail">
        <header class="entry-header page-header">
            <h2 class="entry-title">
                <a href="../post/8464.html" rel="bookmark">Laravel 代码开发最佳实践（持续更新）</a>
            </h2>

            <div class="entry-meta text-muted">
                <span class="posted-on">
                    <i class="glyphicon glyphicon-calendar"></i> Posted on
                    <time class="entry-date published" datetime="2018-02-27T13:28:19+08:00">2018-02-27</time>
                    <time class="updated" datetime="2018-02-27T13:43:38+08:00">2018-02-27 13:43:38</time>
                </span>
                <span class="byline"> by
                    <span class="author vcard">
                        <i class="glyphicon glyphicon-user"></i>
                        <a class="url fn n" href="../author/nonfu">
                            学院君
                        </a>
                    </span>
                </span>
                <span class="article-views">
                    <i class="glyphicon ipt-icon-eye"></i>
                    11102 Views
                </span>
                <span class="comments-link">
                    <i class="glyphicon ipt-icon-bubbles2"></i>
                    <a href="../post/8464.html#comments">
                        1 Comments
                    </a>
                </span>
            </div><!-- .entry-meta -->
        </header><!-- .entry-header -->

        <div class="clearfix"></div>

                                                                                                    <div class="pull-left kb-thumb-medium hidden-xs">
                        <a rel="bookmark" href="../post/8464.html" class="thumbnail">
                            <img width="256" height="128" src="https://static.laravelacademy.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/15196988260350-256x128.png" class="img-rounded wp-post-image" alt=""/>
                        </a>
                    </div>
                                                                                                <div class="kb-thumb-large visible-xs">
                        <a rel="bookmark" href="../post/8464.html" class="thumbnail">
                            <img width="2200" height="200" src="https://static.laravelacademy.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/15196988260350-2200x200.png" class="img wp-post-image" alt="" />
                        </a>
                    </div>
                                    
        <div class="entry entry-excerpt">
            <p>￼

我们这里要讨论的并不是 Laravel 版的 SOLID 原则（想要了解更多 SOLID 原则细节查看这篇文章）亦或是设计模式，而是 Laravel 实际开发中容易被忽略的最佳实践。
内容概览

 	单一职责原则
 	胖模型，瘦控制器
 	验证
 	业务逻辑应该放到服务类
 	DRY（Don&#039;t Repeat Yourself，不要重复造轮子）
 	优先使用 E...</p>
        </div>

